    <briefdescription>
<para>Header file for functions related to applying colorization and hillshading. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="author"><para>Otto Link (<ulink url="mailto:otto.link.bv@gmail.com">otto.link.bv@gmail.com</ulink>) </para>
</simplesect>
This file contains the declarations of functions that are used to apply colorization and hillshading effects to images and arrays. The functions allow for creating grayscale, histogram-based, and colored images from elevation data and other input arrays.</para>
